data.description: Fantastic opportunity to build your dream home in the sought after Golf and Equestrian community of Wedgefield. Bring your own builder or choose one that is working in the area. This lot features 2.16 acres of land to build your dream home. The East Orlando community of Wedgefield offers an 8,500 acre nature preserve on 2 sides of the neighborhood, larger lots, golf, horse trails and more. The Wedgefield golf club is open to the public. Shopping plazas only minutes away. Quick access to Major roads, Medical City and the Airport and only 30 minutes to both downtown Orlando and the beach.
